The terminal UI runtime, ratatui rendering pipeline, slash command system,
input area, and chat view layout are derived from claude-code-rust.
Changes from upstream include:
- Removed the Node.js Agent SDK bridge dependency for non-Anthropic providers.
- Added llama.cpp provider (`src/agent/llama_client.rs`, `src/app/connect/llama_lifecycle.rs`).
- Added Skills loader (`src/skills.rs`), Memory layer (`src/memory.rs`, `src/memory_capture.rs`).
- Added pet character renderer (`src/pet.rs`).
- Rebranded user-visible strings (Claude → Mochi) and welcome banner.
- Disabled startup update checks that pointed to the upstream npm package.

